  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/242330.htm", 
  "description": "<p>受日本“胶囊旅馆”的启发，日本高铁运营公司在高铁内部采用“豆荚”状设计，列车内部为一个个独立的隔间，漫长旅途中，旅客可以在豆荚列车中休息、放松或者四下走动。和低价旅馆类似，旅客可以在列车中充分休息，到达目的地时仍然神清气爽，不带一丝倦意。当然，乘客也不会出现倒时差一样的滞后反应。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2dbcaa02/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242330.htm&amp;t=%E8%B6%A3%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E8%B1%86%E8%8D%9A%E2%80%9D%E7%8A%B6%E5%88%97%E8%BD%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242330.htm&amp;t=%E8%B6%A3%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E8%B1%86%E8%8D%9A%E2%80%9D%E7%8A%B6%E5%88%97%E8%BD%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242330.htm&amp;t=%E8%B6%A3%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E8%B1%86%E8%8D%9A%E2%80%9D%E7%8A%B6%E5%88%97%E8%BD%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242330.htm&amp;t=%E8%B6%A3%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E8%B1%86%E8%8D%9A%E2%80%9D%E7%8A%B6%E5%88%97%E8%BD%A6\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F242330.htm&amp;t=%E8%B6%A3%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%EF%BC%9A%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%98%8E%E2%80%9C%E8%B1%86%E8%8D%9A%E2%80%9D%E